a:17:{s:4:"name";s:10:"Cenforce-D";s:11:"small_descr";s:146:"Cenforce-D is used in the treatment of Erectile Dysfunction with Premature Ejaculation. Cenforce-D contains Sildenafil100 mg and Dapoxetine 60 mg.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:159:"Cenforce-D wird für die Behandlung der erektilen Dysfunktion mit vorzeitiger Ejakulation eingesetzt. Cenforce-D enthält Sildenafil100 mg und 60 mg Dapoxetin.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:165:"Cenforce-D est utilisé dans le traitement de la dysfonction érectile avec l'éjaculation précoce. Cenforce-D contient 100 mg de Sildenafil et 60 mg de Dapoxetine.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:156:"Cenforce-D es usada en el tratamiento de la disfunción eréctil con la eyaculación precoz. Cenforce-D contiene 100 mg de Sildenafil y 60 mg de Dapoxetine.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:0:"";s:10:"full_descr";s:5700:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Cenforce-D is indicated for the treatment of erectile dysfunction in men.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Use Cenforce-D as directed by your doctor.</p><ul><li>Take Cenforce-D by mouth with or without food. Cenforce-D&nbsp;may not work as quickly if you take it with a high-fat meal.</li><li>Cenforce-D is usually taken about 1 hour before sexual activity; however, it may be taken anywhere from 4 hours to a half hour before sexual activity. Talk with your doctor about the best way to take Cenforce-D. Cenforce-D can help you have an erection when sexual stimulation occurs. An erection will not occur just by taking a pill.</li><li>Do not take more than the recommended dose or take it more often than once daily, or as directed by your doctor.</li><li>If you miss a dose of Cenforce-D and you still intend to engage in sexual activity, take it as soon as you remember. Continue to take it as directed by your doctor.</li></ul><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>Take the medication exactly as prescribed by your doctor.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store Cenforce-D at 77 degrees F (25 degrees C). Store away from heat, moisture, and light. Do not store in the bathroom. Keep Cenforce-D out of the reach of children and away from pets.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Active Ingredient: Sildenafil and Dapoxetine.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p><strong>Do NOT use Cenforce-D if:</strong></p><ul><li>you are allergic to any ingredient in <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span></li><li>you have been advised by your doctor to avoid sexual activity because of heart problems</li><li>you are taking nitrates (eg, isosorbide, nitroglycerin) in any form (eg, tablet, capsule, patch, ointment), or nitroprusside</li><li>you use certain recreational drugs called "poppers" (eg, amyl nitrate or nitrite, butyl nitrate or nitrite)</li><li>you take another PDE5 inhibitor (eg, tadalafil, vardenafil) or another medicine that contains sildenafil.</li></ul><p>Contact your doctor or health care provider right away if any of these apply to you.</p><p>Some medical conditions may interact with Cenforce-D. Tell your doctor or pharmacist if you have any medical conditions, especially if any of the following apply to you:</p><ul><li>if you are taking any prescription or nonprescription medicine, herbal preparation, or dietary supplement</li><li>if you have allergies to medicines, foods, or other substances</li><li>if you have a deformed penis (eg, cavernosal fibrosis, Peyronie disease), blood cell problems (eg, leukemia, multiple myeloma, sickle cell anemia), or any other condition that may increase the risk of a prolonged erection (priapism)</li><li>if you have a history of a prolonged (more than 4 hours) or painful erection (priapism)</li><li>if you have a history of certain eye problems (eg, macular degeneration, optic neuropathy, retinitis pigmentosa, sudden vision loss in one or both eyes) or hearing problems (eg, ringing in the ears, decreased hearing, hearing loss)</li><li>if you have a history of liver or kidney problems, lung problems (eg, pulmonary veno-occlusive disease), high or low blood pressure, ulcers, bleeding problems, heart problems (eg, angina, aortic stenosis, heart failure, irregular heartbeat), or blood vessel problems</li><li>if you have a history of heart attack, stroke, or life-threatening irregular heartbeat, especially within the past 6 months.</li></ul><p>Some medicines may interact with Cenforce-D. Tell your health care provider if you are taking any other medicines, especially any of the following:</p><ul><li>Alpha-blockers (eg, doxazosin), medicines for high blood pressure, nitrates (eg, isosorbide, nitroglycerin), or nitroprusside because severe low blood pressure with dizziness, lightheadedness, and fainting may occur</li><li>Azole antifungals (eg, itraconazole, ketoconazole), H<sub>2</sub> antagonists (eg, cimetidine), HIV protease inhibitors (eg, ritonavir, saquinavir), macrolide antibiotics (eg, erythromycin), narcotic analgesics (eg, dihydrocodeine), or telithromycin because they may increase the risk of Cenforce-D's side effects</li><li>Bosentan or rifampin because they may decrease Cenforce-D's effectiveness.</li></ul><p>This may not be a complete list of all interactions that may occur. Ask your health care provider if <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>&nbsp;may interact with other medicines that you take. Check with your health care provider before you start, stop, or change the dose of any medicine.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>All medicines may cause side effects, but many people have no, or minor, side effects.</p><p>Check with your doctor if any of these most common side effects persist or become bothersome:</p><p>Diarrhea; dizziness; flushing; headache; heartburn; stuffy nose; upset stomach.</p><p>Seek medical attention right away if any of these severe side effects occur:</p><p>Severe allergic reactions (rash; hives; itching; difficulty breathing; tightness in the chest; swelling of the mouth, face, lips, or tongue); chest pain; fainting; fast or irregular heartbeat; memory loss; numbness of an arm or leg; one-sided weakness; painful or prolonged erection; ringing in the ears; seizure; severe or persistent dizziness; severe or persistent vision changes; sudden decrease or loss of hearing; sudden decrease or loss of vision in one or both eyes.</p><p>This is not a complete list of all side effects that may occur. If you have questions about side effects, contact your health care provider.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:6589:"<p><strong>INDIKATIONEN</strong><br />Cenforce-D wird f&uuml;r die Behandlung der erektilen Dysfunktion bei M&auml;nnern eingesetzt.<br /><br /><strong>ANLEITUNG</strong><br />Verwenden Sie bitte Cenforce-D wie es von Ihrem Arzt vorgeschrieben ist.<br />Nehmen Sie Cenforce-D oral mit oder ohne Nahrung. Cenforce-D&nbsp;kann nicht so schnell wirken, wenn Sie es mit einer fettreichen Mahlzeit einehmen.<br />Cenforce-D ist in der Regel ca. 1 Stunde vor dem Geschlechtsverkehr einzunehmen, es kann aber von 4 Stunden bis auf eine halbe Stunde vor dem Geschlechtsverkehr eingenommen werden. Beraten Sie sich mit Ihrem Arzt &uuml;ber die beste Art und Weise die Cenforce-D einzunehmen. Cenforce-D kann Ihnen helfen, eine Erektion zu erreichen, wenn sexuelle Stimulation auftritt. Eine Erektion wird nicht lediglich durch die Einnahme einer Pille auftreten.<br />Nehmen Sie bitte nicht mehr als die empfohlene Dosis oder es &ouml;fter als einmal t&auml;glich ein.<br />Wenn Sie eine Dosis von Cenforce-D verpassen und immer noch die Absicht haben, sexuelle Handlungen zu betreiben, nehmen Sie sie ein, sobald Sie sich daran erinnern. Nehmen Sie es weiter ein, wie es von Ihrem Arzt vorgeschrieben wurde.<br /><br /><strong>DOSIERUNG</strong><br />Nehmen Sie das Medikament genau so ein, wie es von Ihrem Arzt verordnet wurde.<br /><br /><strong>AUFBEWAHRUNG</strong><br />Bewahren Sie Cenforce-D bei 77 Grad Fahrenheit (25 Grad C) getrennt von der Hitze, Feuchtigkeit und Licht. Bitte nicht im Badezimmer lagern. Bewahren Sie Cenforce-D au&szlig;erhalb der Reichweite von Kindern und Haustieren auf.<br /><br /><strong>MEHR INFO:</strong><br />&nbsp;Wirkstoff: Sildenafil und Dapoxetin.</p><p><strong>SICHERHEITSHINWEISE</strong></p><p><strong>Verwenden Sie keine Cenforce-D , wenn:</strong><br />Sie allergisch gegen jegliche Zutaten in Cenforce-D sind<br />Es wurde Ihnen von Ihrem Arzt empfohlen, Geschlechtsverkehr wegen den Herzproblemen zu vermeiden<br />Sie Nitrate (z.B. Isosorbid , Nitroglycerin) in irgendeiner Form (zB Tabletten , Kapseln, Pflaster , Salbe ) oder Nitroprussid einnehmen<br />Sie bestimmte Drogen, auch "Poppers" genannt (z. B. Amylacetat Nitrat oder Nitrit -, Butyl- Nitrat oder Nitrit ) verwenden<br />Sie einen anderen PDE5-Hemmer (zB , Tadalafil , Vardenafil ) oder andere Medizin , die Sildenafil enth&auml;lt, einnehmen.<br />Kontaktieren Sie Ihren Arzt oder Arzt sofort, wenn einer dieser Punkte auf Sie zutrifft.<br />Einige medizinische Bedingungen k&ouml;nnen mit Cenforce-D interagieren. Informieren Sie Ihren Arzt oder Apotheker, wenn Sie irgendwelche medizinische Bedingungen haben, vor allem, wenn einer der folgenden Punkte auf Sie zutrifft :<br />wenn Sie verschreibungspflichtige oder nicht verschreibungspflichtige Arzneimitteln, pflanzliche Zubereitung oder Nahrungserg&auml;nzungsmitteln verwenden<br />wenn Sie Allergien gegen Medikamente, Nahrungsmitteln oder andere Substanzen haben<br />wenn Sie einen verformten Penis ( z. B. kavern&ouml;se Fibrose Peyronie -Krankheit), Blutzellen-Erkrankungen (z.B.  Leuk&auml;mie , multiples Myelom, Sichelzellenan&auml;mie) , oder irgendeine andere Bedingung haben, die das Risiko einer verl&auml;ngerten Erektion erh&ouml;hen k&ouml;nnen (Priapismus)<br />wenn Sie eine lange ( mehr als 4 Stunden ) oder schmerzhafte Erektion (Priapismus) haben<br />wenn Sie Augenerkrankungen (z.B. Makuladegeneration, Optikusneuropathie , Retinitis pigmentosa, pl&ouml;tzlicher Verlust des Sehverm&ouml;gens in einem oder beiden Augen) oder Geh&ouml;rprobleme haben (z.B. Klingeln in den Ohren, vermindertes H&ouml;rverm&ouml;gen , H&ouml;rverlust )<br />wenn Sie Leber-oder Nierenprobleme, Lungen-Probleme (z.B. Lungenvenenverschlusskrankheit), hoher oder niedriger Blutdruck , Geschw&uuml;re, Blutungen , Herz-Probleme (z.B. Angina pectoris, Aortenstenose , Herzinsuffizienz, Herzrhythmusst&ouml;rungen ) oder Blutgef&auml;&szlig;probleme haben<br />wenn Sie Herzinfarkt, Schlaganfall oder lebensbedrohliche Herzrhythmusst&ouml;rungen erlebt haben, vor allem innerhalb der letzten 6 Monate.<br /><br />Einige Arzneimittel k&ouml;nnen mit Cenforce-D interagieren. Teilen Sie Ihrem Arzt mit, wenn Sie andere Arzneimitteln , vor allem einer der folgenden einnehmen :<br />Alpha - Blocker (z.B. Doxazosin) , Medikamente gegen Bluthochdruck, Nitrate (z.B. Isosorbid, Nitroglycerin ) oder Nitroprussid , weil dann schwerer Niedrigblutdruck mit Schwindel, Benommenheit und Ohnmacht auftreten k&ouml;nnen<br />Azol-Antimykotika (z.B. Itraconazol, Ketoconazol ) , H2 -Antagonisten ( z. B. Cimetidin ), HIV -Protease-Inhibitoren (z.B. Ritonavir , Saquinavir ), Makrolid- Antibiotika ( z.B. Erythromycin ), Schmerzmitteln (z.B. Dihydrocodein ) oder Telithromycin , weil sie das Risiko der Cenforce-D Nebenwirkungen erh&ouml;hen<br />Bosentan oder Rifampicin, weil sie die Cenforce-D Wirksamkeit verringern.<br /><br />Dies ist nicht eine vollst&auml;ndige Liste aller Interaktionen, die auftreten k&ouml;nnen. Fragen Sie Ihren Arzt, ob Cenforce-D mit anderen Arzneimitteln, die Sie verwenden, interagiert. Lassen Sie sich von Ihrem Arzt beraten, bevor Sie anfangen, aufh&ouml;ren, oder  die Dosis einer Medizin &auml;ndern.</p><p><strong>NEBENWIRKUNGEN</strong></p><p>Alle Arzneimittel k&ouml;nnen Nebenwirkungen haben, allerdings haben viele Menschen keine oder nur geringf&uuml;gige Nebenwirkungen.<br /><br />Lassen Sie sich von Ihrem Arzt beraten, wenn diese am h&auml;ufigsten auftretenden Nebenwirkungen fortbestehen oder als st&ouml;rend empfunden werden:<br /><br />Durchfall, Schwindel, Sp&uuml;lung, Kopfschmerzen, Sodbrennen, verstopfte Nase, Magenverstimmung.<br /><br />Unverz&uuml;glich m&uuml;ssen folgende Nebenwirkungen &Auml;rztlich behandeln werden:<br /><br />Schwere allergische Reaktionen (Hautausschlag , Nesselsucht, Juckreiz, Atembeschwerden , Engegef&uuml;hl in der Brust, Schwellungen im Mund-, Gesichts-, Lippen oder Zunge), Schmerzen in der Brust , Ohnmacht, schneller oder unregelm&auml;&szlig;iger Herzschlag, Ged&auml;chtnisverlust , Taubheitsgef&uuml;hl in einem Arm oder Bein ; einseitige Schw&auml;che, schmerzhafte oder verl&auml;ngerte Erektion , Klingeln in den Ohren; Beschlagnahme , schweren oder anhaltenden Schwindel, schweren oder anhaltenden Sehst&ouml;rungen, pl&ouml;tzliche Abnahme oder Verlust des Geh&ouml;rs ; pl&ouml;tzliche Abnahme oder Verlust des Sehverm&ouml;gens in einem oder beiden Augen.<br /><br />Dies ist keine vollst&auml;ndige Liste aller Nebenwirkungen, die auftreten k&ouml;nnen. Wenn Sie weitere Fragen zu Nebenwirkungen haben, kontaktieren Sie Ihren Arzt.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:21287:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr">Cenforce-D&nbsp;<span class="hps alt-edited">est indiqu&eacute;e pour le</span> <span class="hps">traitement de la dysfonction</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&eacute;rectile aux hommes</span><span>.</span> </span></p><p><strong>A</strong><strong>DMINISTRATION</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Utilisez</span>&nbsp;</span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">selon les directions de votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Prenez</span> Cenforce-D&nbsp;<span class="hps">par voie orale avec</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou sans aliment</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Elle</span> <span class="hps">peut ne pas fonctionner</span> <span class="hps">aussi rapidement</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">si vous la prenez</span> <span class="hps">avec un repas</span> <span class="hps">riche en graisses.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps"><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>&nbsp;est</span> <span class="hps">g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement prise 1</span> <span class="hps">heure avant l'activit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">sexuelle</span><span>, mais</span> <span class="hps">il peut &ecirc;tre pris</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; partir de</span> <span class="hps">4 heures &agrave; une</span> <span class="hps">demi-heure</span> <span class="hps">avant l'activit&eacute; sexuelle</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Discutez avec votre</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">m&eacute;decin la meilleure</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">fa&ccedil;on d'utilisaton de</span> Cenforce-D<span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps"><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span> peut</span> <span class="hps">vous aider &agrave; avoir</span> <span class="hps">une &eacute;rection</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pendant la stimulation sexuelle</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Une &eacute;rection</span> <span class="hps">ne se produira pas</span> <span class="hps">juste en prenant</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">un comprim&eacute;</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne prenez pas plus</span> <span class="hps">que la dose recommand&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited"> plus souvent</span> <span class="hps">qu'une fois par jour</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">prenez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span> selon </span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les directions de votre m&eacute;decin</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">manquez une dose de</span> Cenforce-D&nbsp;<span class="hps">et vous avez toujours</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'intention d'avoir</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une activit&eacute; sexuelle</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">prenez-la d&egrave;s</span> <span class="hps">que vous vous souvenez</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Continuez &agrave; la</span> <span class="hps">prendre comme dirig&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">par votre m&eacute;decin.</span></span></li></ul><p><strong><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">DOSAGE</span></span></strong></p><p><span lang="fr"><span class="hps">Prenez le m&eacute;dicament exactement selon la prescription de votre m&eacute;decin.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><strong>CONSERVATION</strong></p><p>Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps"><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span></span></span> &agrave; <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">77 degr&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">F (25</span> <span class="hps">degr&eacute;s C).</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>&nbsp;</span></span>Entreposez   loin de la chaleur et l'humidit&eacute;. Ne gardez pas dans la salle de    bain. Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>&nbsp;hors de la port&eacute;e des enfants et loin des animaux.</p><p><strong>INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</strong><br /><br />L'ingr&eacute;dient actif: Sildenafil and Dapoxetine.</p><p><span lang="fr"><span class="hps">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong>N'utilisez pas Cenforce-D si:</strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous &ecirc;tes allergique</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span></span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez &eacute;t&eacute; inform&eacute;</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">par votre m&eacute;decin pour</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&eacute;viter l'activit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">sexuelle &agrave; cause de</span> <span class="hps">probl&egrave;mes cardiaques</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous prenez</span> des<span class="hps"> nitrate</span>s <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, isosorbide,</span> <span class="hps">nitroglyc&eacute;rine) sous</span> <span class="hps atn alt-edited">des formes differentes (</span><span class="alt-edited">par exemple, un comprim&eacute;</span><span class="alt-edited">, une g&eacute;lule,</span><span class="alt-edited"> une pommade)</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps">nitroprusside</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">vous</span> <span class="hps">utilisez</span> <span class="hps">certains</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;dicaments</span> <span class="hps">r&eacute;cr&eacute;ationnels</span> <span class="hps">appel&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">poppers</span> <span class="hps">(</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>par exemple</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>,</span> <span class="hps">le</span> <span class="hps atn">nitrate ou </span></span>nitrite <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps atn">d'</span><span>amyle</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">le</span> <span class="hps">nitrate</span> ou </span>nitrite<span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">de butyle</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous prenez un autre</span> <span class="hps">inhibiteur de </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">5</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">PDE</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>tadalafil, vardenafil<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>)</span> <span class="hps">ou un autre m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps">qui contient</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">sild&eacute;nafil.</span></span></li></ul><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Contactez votre m&eacute;decin</span> <span class="hps">imm&eacute;diatement si l'un</span> <span class="hps">de ces</span> <span class="hps">cas</span> <span class="hps">s'applique &agrave; vous</span><span>.</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Certaines conditions <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">m&eacute;dicales</span></span></span> <span class="hps">peuvent interagir avec</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">Cenforce-D.</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Dites &agrave;</span> <span class="hps"><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">votre m&eacute;decin</span></span></span> <span class="hps">si vous</span> <span class="hps">avez des conditions m&eacute;dicales suivantes</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">surtout si une des</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">conditions suivantes s'applique &agrave;</span> <span class="hps">vous:</span></span></p><ul><li>si vous prenez une ordonnance ou un m&eacute;dicament en vente libre, une pr&eacute;paration d'herbes ou un suppl&eacute;ment alimentaire</li><li>si vous avez des allergies aux m&eacute;dicaments, aliments ou autres substances</li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si votre </span><span class="hps">p&eacute;nis est d&eacute;form&eacute;</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span>,</span> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">la scl&eacute;rose des corps caverneux, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">la maladie de Peyronie</span><span>)</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> les probl&egrave;mes</span> <span class="hps atn">de cellules sanguines (</span><span>par exemple</span><span>,</span> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">la leuc&eacute;mie</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">le my&eacute;lome multiple, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">l'an&eacute;mie falciforme</span><span>)</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">ou toute</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">autre condition qui </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">peut</span> <span class="hps">augmenter le risque</span> <span class="hps">d'une</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;rection prolong&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span class="alt-edited">le priapisme</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous avez</span> <span class="hps">une histoire</span> <span class="hps">d'une</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;rection prolong&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>plus de 4 heures</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps atn">ou douloureuse (</span><span class="alt-edited">le priapisme</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous avez</span> <span class="hps">une histoire</span> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">certains probl&egrave;mes oculaires</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>la d&eacute;g&eacute;n&eacute;rescence maculaire, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">la neuropathie optique</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">la r&eacute;tinite pigmentaire</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">l'&eacute;clipse visuelle</span><span>) </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>ou</span> <span class="hps">des probl&egrave;mes d'audition</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>exemple</span><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited"> le bourdonnement dans les oreilles</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">,</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">la diminution auditive</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">,</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">l'abolition de l'oule</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable">si vous</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">avez des histoires de</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable">probl&egrave;mes h&eacute;patiques ou r&eacute;naux</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">des probl&egrave;mes des pumons</span> <span class="hps atn gt-trans-draggable">(</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">par exemple,</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">la lesion occlusive de veins</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">)</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="gt-trans-draggable">la pression</span> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">art&eacute;rielle &eacute;lev&eacute;e ou basse</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, les ulc&egrave;res</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable">des probl&egrave;mes </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable">d'</span></span>h&eacute;morragie<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, les probl&egrave;mes cardiaques </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps atn gt-trans-draggable">(</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">par exemple</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited"> </span></span>l'angine,<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited"> la st&eacute;nose aortique</span><span class="gt-trans-draggable">, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">l'attaque cardiaque,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">le rythme cardiaque irr&eacute;gulier) ou</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited"> des probl&egrave;mes de vaisseaux sanguins</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">avez des histoires de</span> <span class="hps">crise cardiaque,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">d'accident vasculaire c&eacute;r&eacute;bral</span><span>,</span> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr">ou les </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited">probl&egrave;mes </span></span><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">s&eacute;v&egrave;res de</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps gt-trans-draggable alt-edited"> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">rythme cardiaque irr&eacute;gulier </span></span><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">en particulier</span> <span class="hps">au cours des 6</span> <span class="hps">derniers mois</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Certains m&eacute;dicaments peuvent interagir avec <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>.  Informez votre  m&eacute;decin si vous prenez d'autres m&eacute;dicaments, en  particulier les &eacute;l&eacute;ments  suivants:</p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Les alpha-bloquants</span> <span class="hps">(p. ex</span><span class="alt-edited">, doxazosine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des m&eacute;dicaments pour le traitement </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">d'hypertension</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>les nitrates</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, isosorbide</span><span class="alt-edited">, nitroglyc&eacute;rine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou nitroprussiate</span> <span class="hps">parce</span> que <span class="hps alt-edited">l'hypotension s&eacute;v&egrave;re</span> <span class="hps">avec </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">le vertige</span><span>, l'&eacute;tourdissement</span> <span class="hps">et l'&eacute;vanouissement</span> <span class="hps">peut se produire</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Les antifongiques de type azole</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple,</span> <span class="hps">itraconazole</span><span>)</span><span>,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> l</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">es antagonistes de H2</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, </span></span>cimetidine<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>)</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">, les inhibiteurs de prot&eacute;ase</span> <span class="hps">du VIH </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, ritonavi</span></span>r, saquinavir<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>)</span><span>, les antibiotiques </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>macrolides</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&eacute;rythromycine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">les analg&eacute;siques</span> <span class="hps">narcotiques (par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, dihydrocod&eacute;ine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>ou</span> <span class="hps">t&eacute;lithromycine</span><span>, car ils peuvent</span> <span class="hps">augmenter le</span> <span class="hps">risque d'effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de&nbsp;Cenforce-D</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Bosentan ou rifampin</span><span>, car il</span> <span class="hps">peut diminuer l'efficacit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">de Cenforce-D</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">.</span></span></li></ul><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Ce n'est pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une liste compl&egrave;te</span> <span class="hps">de toutes les interactions qui peuvent se produire. </span></span>Consultez votre <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">m&eacute;decin</span></span> si Cenforce-D peut interagir avec d'autres m&eacute;dicaments que vous prenez. V&eacute;rifiez avec votre <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">m&eacute;decin</span></span> avant de d&eacute;marrer, d'arr&ecirc;ter ou modifier la dose de tout m&eacute;dicament.</p><p><strong>LES EFFETS SECONDAIRES</strong></p><p>Tout les m&eacute;dicaments peuvent causer des effets secondaires, mais        beaucoup de gens n'ont pas, ou ont des effets secondaires mineurs.</p><p>Consultez votre m&eacute;decin si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables persiste ou devient g&ecirc;nant:</p><p>La diarrh&eacute;e; l'&eacute;tourdissement; le rougissement; le mal &agrave; la t&ecirc;te; la br&ucirc;lure; le nez bouch&eacute;; l'indigestion.</p><p>Consultez votre m&eacute;decin imm&eacute;diatement si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables s&eacute;v&egrave;res se produit:</p><p>Les r&eacute;actions allergiques graves (l'urticaire, l'&eacute;ruption cutan&eacute;e, la       d&eacute;mangeaison, la difficult&eacute; &agrave; respirer, la sensation d'oppression  dans      la poitrine, l'enflure de la bouche, du visage, des l&egrave;vres ou  de la      langue); la douleur dans la poitrine; l'&eacute;vanouissement; le  rythme cardiaque rapide ou irr&eacute;gulier; l'amn&eacute;sie; l'engourdissement d'un  bras ou d'une jambe; l'engourdissement d'une partie du corps; l'<span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">&eacute;rection prolong&eacute;e et douloureuse; </span></span>le bourdonnement d'oreille; des crises d'&eacute;pilepsie; <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited"> </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">l'&eacute;tourdissement</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">grave ou persistant; </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">des changements de vision</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">s&eacute;v&egrave;res ou persistants</span><span class="alt-edited">; </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="alt-edited">la </span></span>duret&eacute; d'oreille<span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="alt-edited">l'abolition de l'oule;</span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="alt-edited"> la diminution</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou l'&eacute;clipse visuelle</span> <span class="hps">d'un</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&oelig;il ou des deux yeux.</span></span></p><p>Ce n'est pas une liste compl&egrave;te de tout les effets secondaires qui        peuvent survenir. Si vous avez des questions sur des effets        ind&eacute;sirables, contactez votre m&eacute;decin.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:7295:"<p><strong>INDICACIONES</strong></p><p>Cenforce-D&nbsp;es indicada para el tratamiento de la disfunci&oacute;n er&eacute;ctil masculina.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCCIONES</strong></p><p>Utilice Cenforce-D como es indicado por el m&eacute;dico.</p><ul><li>Tome Cenforce-D por v&iacute;a oral con o sin alimentos. Viagra podr&iacute;a no funcionar lo m&aacute;s r&aacute;pidamente si es tomada con una comida rica en grasas.</li><li>Generalmente Cenforce-D es tomada aproximadamente 1 hora&nbsp; antes de la actividad sexual, pero, puede ser tomada desde 4 horas a una media hora antes de la actividad sexual. Es necesario de hablar con el m&eacute;dico sobre la mejor manera de toma de Cenforce-D. Cenforce-D puede ayudar a obtener una erecci&oacute;n cuando ocurra la estimulaci&oacute;n sexual. Una erecci&oacute;n no ocurrir&aacute; solamente tomando una pastilla.</li><li>No tome m&aacute;s de la dosis recomendada o no lo tome con m&aacute;s frecuencia que una vez al d&iacute;a; tome como es indicado por m&eacute;dico.</li><li>Si usted olvida de tomar una dosis de Cenforce-D&nbsp;pero tiene la intenci&oacute;n de participar en la actividad sexual, t&oacute;mela tan pronto como usted recuerde. Contin&uacute;e a tomarla como es indicado por el m&eacute;dico.</li></ul><p><strong>DOSIS</strong></p><p>Tome el medicamento exactamente seg&uacute;n las prescriptiones de su m&eacute;dico.</p><p><strong>ALMACENAMIENTO&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Almacene Cenforce-D en 77 grados F (25 grados C). Almacene lejos del calor, de la humedad y de la luz. No lo guarde en el ba&ntilde;o. Mantiena Cenforce-D lejos de los ninos y lejos de los animales.</p><p><strong>INFORMACI&Oacute;N DE SEGURIDAD</strong></p><p><strong>NO use Cenforce-D si:</strong></p><ul><li>Usted es al&eacute;rgico a cualquier ingrediente de <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span></li><li>su m&eacute;dico recomienda a evitar la actividad sexual a causa de problemas card&iacute;acos</li><li>Usted&nbsp;toma los nitratos (por ejemplo, isosorbide, nitroglicerina) en cualquiera forma (por ejemplo, tableta, c&aacute;psula, ung&uuml;ento) o nitroprusiato</li><li>Usted&nbsp;usa ciertas drogas recreativas llamadas "poppers" (por ejemplo, nitrato de amilo o nitrito, nitrato de butilo o nitrito)</li><li>Usted&nbsp;toma otro inhibidor de FDE5 (por ejemplo, tadalafil, vardenafil) o alg&uacute;n otro medicamento que contiene sildenafilo.</li></ul><p>Contacte con su m&eacute;dico de una vez si alguna de estas condici&oacute;nes se aplique a usted.</p><p>Algunas condiciones m&eacute;dicas pueden interactuar con <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>. D&iacute;ga a su m&eacute;dico o farmac&eacute;utico si tiene algunas de las siguientes condici&oacute;nes m&eacute;dicas:</p><ul><li>si toma cualquier medicamento recetado o medicamento sin receta, preparado herb&aacute;ceo o suplemento diet&eacute;tico</li><li>si usted tiene alergias a medicamentos, alimentos o otras sustancias</li><li>si usted tiene un pene deforme (por ejemplo, fibrosis cavernosa, enfermedad de Peyronie), los problemas de las c&eacute;lulas sangu&iacute;neas (por ejemplo, leucemia, mieloma m&uacute;ltiple, anemia de c&eacute;lulas falciformes), o otra condici&oacute;n que puede aumentar el riesgo de una erecci&oacute;n prolongada (priapismo)</li><li>si usted tiene antecedentes de una erecci&oacute;n prolongada (m&aacute;s de 4 horas) o dolorosa (priapismo)</li><li>si usted tiene antecedentes de problemas de la vista (por ejemplo, degeneraci&oacute;n macular, neuropat&iacute;a &oacute;ptica, retinitis pigmentosa, p&eacute;rdida repentina de visi&oacute;n en uno o ambos ojos) o problemas de audici&oacute;n (por ejemplo, zumbido en los o&iacute;dos, disminuci&oacute;n de la audici&oacute;n, p&eacute;rdida de la audici&oacute;n)</li><li>si usted tiene antecedentes de problemas hep&aacute;ticos o renales, problemas pulmonares (por ejemplo, enfermedad pulmonar veno-oclusiva hep&aacute;tica), presi&oacute;n arterial alta o baja, &uacute;lceras, problemas de sangrado, problemas card&iacute;acos (por ejemplo, angina de pecho, la estenosis a&oacute;rtica, insuficiencia card&iacute;aca, ritmo card&iacute;aco irregular) , o los problemas de los vasos sangu&iacute;neos</li><li>si usted tiene un antecedente de ataque card&iacute;aco, accidente cerebrovascular, o arritmias amenazantes a la vida, especialmente en los &uacute;ltimos 6 meses.</li></ul><p>Algunos medicamentos pueden interactuar con <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span>. D&iacute;ga a su m&eacute;dico si toma otros medicamentos, especialmente cualquier de los siguientes:</p><ul><li>&nbsp;Los alfa-bloqueadores (por ejemplo, doxazosina), medicamentos para la presi&oacute;n arterial alta, los nitratos (por ejemplo, isosorbide, nitroglicerina), o nitroprusiato porque la presi&oacute;n arterial muy baja, con mareos, vah&iacute;dos y desmayos pueden ocurrir</li><li>Antif&uacute;ngicos azoles (por ejemplo, itraconazol, ketoconazol), los antagonistas H2 (por ejemplo, cimetidina), inhibidores de la proteasa del VIH (por ejemplo, ritonavir, saquinavir), antibi&oacute;ticos macr&oacute;lidos (por ejemplo, eritromicina), analg&eacute;sicos narc&oacute;ticos (por ejemplo, la dihidrocode&iacute;na), o telitromicina porque ellos pueden aumentar el riesgo de efectos secundarios de <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span></li><li>Bosentan o rifampicina, porque pueden disminuir la eficacia de Cenforce-D.</li></ul><p>No es una lista completa de todas las interacciones que pueden ocurrir. Pregunte a su m&eacute;dico si <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cenforce-D</span></span> puede interaccionar con otros medicamentos que toma. Consulte con su m&eacute;dico antes de iniciar, detener o cambiar la dosis de cualquier medicamento.</p><p><strong>EFECTOS SECUNDARIOS</strong></p><p>Todos los medicamentos pueden causar efectos secundarios, pero muchas personas no tienen estos efectos, o tienen efectos secundarios menores.</p><p>Consulte con su m&eacute;dico si cualquier de estos efectos secundarios m&aacute;s comunes persiste o vuelve molesto:</p><p>Diarrea, mareos, enrojecimiento, dolor de cabeza, pirosis, congesti&oacute;n nasal, dispepsia.</p><p>Busque atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica inmediatamente si alguno de estos efectos secundarios graves ocurre:</p><p>Las reacciones al&eacute;rgicas graves (erupci&oacute;n cut&aacute;nea, urticaria, picaz&oacute;n, dificultad para respirar, opresi&oacute;n en el pecho, hinchaz&oacute;n de la boca, cara, labios o lengua), dolor de pecho, desmayos, latido del coraz&oacute;n r&aacute;pido o irregular, p&eacute;rdida de memoria, adormecimiento de un brazo o una pierna , debilidad unilateral; erecci&oacute;n dolorosa o prolongada, zumbido en los o&iacute;dos, convulsiones, mareos severos o persistentes, cambios en la visi&oacute;n severos o persistentes, disminuci&oacute;n o p&eacute;rdida repentina de la audici&oacute;n; disminuci&oacute;n o p&eacute;rdida repentina de la visi&oacute;n en uno o ambos ojos.</p><p>No es una lista completa de efectos secundarios que pueden ocurrir. Si usted tiene preguntas sobre los efectos secundarios, contacte con el m&eacute;dico.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:6:"2.7846";s:9:"pack_name";s:5:"pills";s:4:"type";s:2:"mg";s:7:"analogs";a:5:{s:18:"Extra Super Viagra";s:20:"Erectile Dysfunction";s:13:"Kamagra Super";s:20:"